Step 1 : Install aws and terraform in your PC

Step 2: Configure aws user in your PC

Step 3: Once done, Above step fo to directory where task.tf is stored

--> Followe this blog for above steps: https://ghumare64.medium.com/terraform-is-a-secret-towards-cloud-automation-%EF%B8%8F-f9c9463b0304
--> Change the profile name in code as per your IAM user

here: 
provider "aws" {
  region  = "ap-south-1"
  profile = "Rohit" <------------- Change this IAM user
}


Step 4: Run following commands

--> $ terraform init
--> $ terraform plan
--> $ terraform apply --auto-approve
